WEBVTT

00:09:58.600 --> 00:10:00.936
networks, mentoring, trainings.

00:10:00.960 --> 00:10:02.160
All is good.

00:10:03.320 --> 00:10:05.256
But it is these two decisions

00:10:05.280 --> 00:10:09.296
that at the end of the day
send the most powerful change signal

00:10:09.320 --> 00:10:10.840
in any organization.

00:10:13.040 --> 00:10:16.096
Now, I never set out
to be a diversity advocate.

00:10:16.120 --> 00:10:17.840
I am a business advisor.

00:10:18.720 --> 00:10:23.696
But now my goal is
to change the face of leadership,

00:10:23.720 --> 00:10:25.160
to make it more diverse --

00:10:26.080 --> 00:10:28.576
and not so that leaders can check a box

00:10:28.600 --> 00:10:31.576
and feel like they have
complied with something